ng Bùi Đạo Châu thủ trát, suất nhĩ khiển hứng, ký cận trình Tô Hoán thị ngự - 暮秋枉裴道州手札，率爾遣興，寄近呈蘇渙侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-45/poem-4eJywbt-l3JBtnQS2cCKjA">Thủ 45 - 首４５</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Trung-ti%C3%AAu/poem-ZO9Ll4-vbJGIH7lq4nlJ7g">Trung tiêu - 中宵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%AD-l%C4%83ng-ch%C3%A2u-ca/poem-d_PQxwC70LelXYh2r5t1vQ">Tử lăng châu ca - 紫菱洲歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%C3%A3n-thi%E1%BA%BFp-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-th%E1%BB%8B/poem-DMwmsQj2LEjUcnyM_Px3fA">Vãn thiếp Phạm thị - 輓妾范氏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
